@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@plotId = demo_stage5_plot_example
@recordId = demo_stage5_record_example
@alertId = demo_stage5_alert_example
@imagePath = ./sample.jpg

### Single image detection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/detect/image
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----AgriBoundary

------AgriBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< {{imagePath}}
------AgriBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="plot_id"

{{plotId}}
------AgriBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="source_type"

manual_upload
------AgriBoundary--

### Mobile overview, user_id is reserved and currently does not filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/overview?user_id=demo_user

### Mobile plots
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/plots?user_id=demo_user

### Mobile plot detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/plots/{{plotId}}

### Mobile record detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/records/{{recordId}}

### Legacy mobile alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/alerts

### Mobile suggestion
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mobile/suggestions/{{recordId}}

### Alert list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts?page=1&page_size=20

### Resolve alert with demo audit fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/{{alertId}}/resolve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operator_id": "demo_user",
  "operator_name": "演示用户",
  "note": "已通知农技人员复核"
}

### Alert action history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alerts/{{alertId}}/actions
